swDdmMIB.name: swDdmMIB
swDdmMIB.description: The structure of DDM for the proprietary enterprise.

swDdmTrapState.name: swDdmTrapState
swDdmTrapState.description: This object indicates the trap action state.

swDdmLogState.name: swDdmLogState
swDdmLogState.description: This object indicates the log action state.

swDdmStatusTable.name: swDdmStatusTable
swDdmStatusTable.description: This table contains the DDM status information.

swDdmStatusEntry.name: swDdmStatusEntry
swDdmStatusEntry.description: This is an entry of the swDdmStatusTable.

swDdmTemperature.name: swDdmTemperature
swDdmTemperature.description: This object indicates the real time value of the temperature. As the value is a floating point data type, the DisplayString type is used to define this parameter.

swDdmVoltage.name: swDdmVoltage
swDdmVoltage.description: This object indicates the real time value of the supply voltage. As the value value is a floating point data type, the DisplayString type is used to define this parameter.

swDdmBiasCurrent.name: swDdmBiasCurrent
swDdmBiasCurrent.description: This object indicates the real time value of the tx bias.

swDdmTxPower.name: swDdmTxPower
swDdmTxPower.description: This object indicates the real time value of the tx power. As the value is a floating point data type, the DisplayString type is used to define this parameter.

swDdmRxPower.name: swDdmRxPower
swDdmRxPower.description: This object indicates the real time value of the rx power. As the value is a floating data type, the DisplayString type is used to define this parameter.

swDdmThresholdMgmtTable.name: swDdmThresholdMgmtTable
swDdmThresholdMgmtTable.description: This table contains DDM temperature configuration information.

swDdmThresholdMgmtEntry.name: swDdmThresholdMgmtEntry
swDdmThresholdMgmtEntry.description: This is an entry of the swDdmConfigThresholdTable.

swDdmThresholdType.name: swDdmThresholdType
swDdmThresholdType.description: This object indicates the threshold type.

swDdmHighAlarm.name: swDdmHighAlarm
swDdmHighAlarm.description: This object indicates the high alarm threshold value to be configured. As the value is a floating point data type, the DisplayString type is used to define this parameter.

swDdmLowAlarm.name: swDdmLowAlarm
swDdmLowAlarm.description: This object indicates the low alarm threshold value to be configured. As the value is a floating data type, the DisplayString type is used to define this parameter.

swDdmHighWarning.name: swDdmHighWarning
swDdmHighWarning.description: This object indicates the high warning threshold value to be configured. As the value is a floating data type, the DisplayString type is used to define this parameter.

swDdmLowWarning.name: swDdmLowWarning
swDdmLowWarning.description: This object indicates the low warning threshold value to be configured. As the value is a floating data type, the DisplayString type is used to define this parameter.

swDdmActionMgmtTable.name: swDdmActionMgmtTable
swDdmActionMgmtTable.description: This table contains the configuration of the action taken when any parameter exceeds its threshold.

swDdmActionMgmtEntry.name: swDdmActionMgmtEntry
swDdmActionMgmtEntry.description: This is an entry of the swDdmConfigActionTable.

swDdmActionType.name: swDdmActionType
swDdmActionType.description: This object indicates the action type.

swDdmShutdown.name: swDdmShutdown
swDdmShutdown.description: This object indicates the shutdown action. The value 'other' means that the port does not support DDM.

swDdmTrapAndLog.name: swDdmTrapAndLog
swDdmTrapAndLog.description: This object indicates the trap and log action. The value 'other' means that the port does not support DDM.

swDdmPortMgmtTable.name: swDdmPortMgmtTable
swDdmPortMgmtTable.description: This table contains the configuration of the DDM state and shutdown mode when any parameter exceeds its threshold.

swDdmPortMgmtEntry.name: swDdmPortMgmtEntry
swDdmPortMgmtEntry.description: This is an entry of the swDdmPortMgmtTable.

swDdmPortState.name: swDdmPortState
swDdmPortState.description: This object indicates the DDM state information by port.

swDdmPortShutdown.name: swDdmPortShutdown
swDdmPortShutdown.description: This object indicates whether or not to shutdown the port on which the operating parameter exceeds the specified threshold.

swDdmAlarmTrap.name: swDdmAlarmTrap
swDdmAlarmTrap.description: The trap is sent when any parameter value exceeds the alarm threshold value or recover to normal status depending on the configuration of the trap action.

swDdmWarningTrap.name: swDdmWarningTrap
swDdmWarningTrap.description: The trap is sent when any parameter value exceeds the warning threshold value or recover to normal status depending on the configuration of the trap action.

swDdmThresholdExceedType.name: swDdmThresholdExceedType
swDdmThresholdExceedType.description: This object is used by swDdmAlarmTrap and swDdmWarningTrap to indicate if the threshold that was exceeded was a high threshold or a low threshold.

swDdmThresholdExceedOrRecover.name: swDdmThresholdExceedOrRecover
swDdmThresholdExceedOrRecover.description: This object is used by swDdmAlarmTrap and swDdmWarningTrap,to indicate the GBIC is exceeding its ddm threshold or recover to normal status.
